                        <div class="media-body">
                            <h4 class="media-heading"><a href="#">QPR Suicide Triage Training for First Responders</a></h4>

                            <p>
                                4-8 hour training for first responders on assessing suicide risk level. Recommended for first responders ages 18+.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="iconBox type3">
                    <div class="media">
                        <a class="pull-left" href="#">
