                        </a>

                        <div class="media-body">
                            <h4 class="media-heading"><a href="#">QPRT Suicide Risk Assessment and Management Training Program</a></h4>

                            <p>
                                An 8-10 hour training for caregivers, health care providers, and mental health professionals treating those patients at elevated risk for suicidal behaviors while improving their detection, assessment, and management skills in all settings and across
